        {
            "title": "百度據悉考慮讓AI晶片子公司昆侖芯赴香港上市",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國在研發輝達競品方面的嘗試引發投資者興趣之際，據知情人士稱，百度正在考慮讓旗下人工智能(AI)晶片業務昆侖芯在香港上市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，對昆侖芯的估值為至少30億美元。他們還表示，相關討論尚處於早期階段，IPO的時間和規模等細節尚不確定。由於事未公開，知情人士要求匿名。昆侖芯生產數據中心伺服器晶片。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在路透社率先報導了這一IPO計畫後，百度股價周五在香港一度上漲7.8%，創9月17日以來最大漲幅。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2af02945-98e1-3dbc-b987-d02a862137a7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">百度尚未回覆通過郵件發送的置評請求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Baidu Is Said to Weigh Hong Kong IPO for AI Chip Unit Kunlunxin</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Charlotte Yang.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%AE%93ai%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E5%AD%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%98%86%E4%BE%96%E8%8A%AF%E8%B5%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-072534049.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 16:20:56",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
